This is the Debian/GNU prepackaged version of SEAM, the simple extendable
abstract machine.  SEAM was developed at the Programming Systems Lab,
Saarland University, Saarbrücken, Germany.

The Debian package was put together by Marco Kuhlmann <mk@debian.org> using
sources obtained from

    http://www.ps.uni-sb.de/alice/

Changes with respect to the original source:

    * added Debian-specific scripts and control files

